        <Summary>A Tetris-like "action game" for two players</Summary>
        <Description>Blobtrix only be played on a LAN or on the Internet. Blobtrix differs from the original Tetris by many ways. Firstly, it is two-sided. One player plays upwards and the other downwards. Secondly, the game isn't so slow - the faster player with more skill wins. The possible speeds go from slow and relaxing to the level in which you really have to trust your instincts.</Description>
